# TITLE: Title Appointment System

## PURPOSE:
- The Purpose of this application is to provide a mechanism for scheduling appointments between
- the company's customers and contacts.

# AUTHOR INFORMATION
- Author: Amanda Parrotta
- Email:  aparr01@wgu.edu
- Application version 1
- Date: May 30th, 2022

# RUN INFORMATION
- IDE: IntelliJ IDEA 2021.1 (Community Edition)
- JDK: 17.0.1
- JavaFX SDK: javafx-sdk-17.0.1
- JDBC: jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/client_schedule?connectionTimeZone=SERVER"
- Add VM Options : --module-path ${PATH_TO_FX} --add-modules javafx.fxml,javafx.controls,javafx.graphics

# REPORT INFORMATION
- The additional report I chose to include is a display of all the appointments modified by a user.

# MySQL Connector
- mysql-connector-java-8.0.25